value:
WITH languages, language_type, groupIds 
FOR e IN language_type 
    FOR gid in groupIds
        FILTER gid._key == "375608"
 
RETURN gid
name: playingedges

value:
WITH languages, ofLanguage, groupIds 
FOR gid IN groupIds
    FILTER gid.key.groupIdValue == @groupId
    FOR l IN 1..1 OUTBOUND gid ofLanguage
        FILTER l.value == @language
        RETURN gid
name: findGroupIdByKey

value:
WITH groupIds, ofGroupId, artifactIds
FOR aid in artifactIds
// may need inner join ex FILTER doc1.`attribute` == doc2.`attribute`
    FILTER aid.key.artifactIdValue == @artifactId
    FOR gid IN 1..1 OUTBOUND aid ofGroupId
        FILTER gid.key.groupIdValue == @groupId
            AND gid.key.language == @language
        RETURN aid
name: findArtifactIdByKey

value:
WITH ofLanguage, groupIds, artifactIds
FOR ofl IN ofLanguage
    FILTER ofl._to == @languageId
    AND ofl._from == @groupId
    RETURN ofl
name: findOfLanguageByVertexIds

value:

value:
WITH ofArtifactId, artifactIds, versions
FOR ofAid IN ofArtifactId
    FILTER ofAid._to == @artifactId
    AND ofAid._from == @version
    RETURN ofAid
name: getOfArtifactIdByVertexIds

value:
WITH artifactIds, ofArtifactId, versions
FOR v IN versions
    FILTER v.key.versionValue == @versionId
    FOR aid in 1..1 OUTBOUND v ofArtifactId
        FILTER aid.key.groupIdValue == @groupId
            AND aid.key.artifactIdValue == @artifactId
            AND aid.key.language == @language
        RETURN v
name: getVersionByKey

value:
WITH artifacts
FOR a IN artifacts
    FILTER a.key.groupIdValue == @groupIdId
        AND a.key.artifactIdValue == @artifactIdId
        AND a.key.version == @versionId
        AND a.key.packaging == @packagingId
        AND a.key.language == @languageId
    RETURN a
name: getArtifactByKey
